      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GIVE ME ROOM (1) improved her time on first attempt this course and distance with a 3.5 lengths win in 17.40 here latest. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. CHAROS JOURNEY (2) has a strong record this trip including four wins from seven starts. Recorded a 5 length win (17.37) in a Grade 6 last time at this track. Can feature with the right run. TOPPER TENACIOUS (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 17.68. Outside box to overcome but has the ability and in winning form. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Sure to be thereabouts. ARCTIC CROP (3) was a huge winner last start. Sure to run well again.",
